node.text: Idk WHAT I was doin with this beard but HEY, OVERRUN comes out tomorrow, August 17th. WATCH IT IF YOU LIKE BEING ENTERTAINED WITH KICKASS STUNTS AND EXPLOSIONS of both fire and emotions. Gas. Also BRUCE MF DERN. Enough said. Thanks to my boy @josh.tessier for being a badass ever since we met on Thundermans. His company @turbopandaproductions for making it happen. And @omidzader for being a killer lead to this film and a great friend on and off screen!! Let’s run it back 🤠😻👻 @overrunfilm @strikebackstudios

node.text: Live your life now! It’s so easy to get caught up in our plans to “succeed” in the eyes of the world and we lose sight of the present moment. The gift. I can lose track of what really makes me actually happy sometimes. I think we should do that first, and the rest will follow. The rest of your life, or like Billy Joel sings, “Vienna”, will wait for you! So feed the inner child first. I think that voice is smarter than we give it credit. Because when it’s all said and done, you can get what you want or you can just get old.. 🤍

node.text: The Pretty Grit, this project we’ve  been working on for over a year, it came out of a place of real pain. A deep hurt I hadn’t felt in life before. I started a band and this was the first song we wrote. The Pretty Grit is about flipping your circumstances. Taking something so gritty and shitty and turning it into something beautiful. And that’s really what art means to me, personally. That’s Pretty Grit. I’m so excited to set out on this journey with my five brothers @theprettygrit @cocoonmalibu GO WATCH THE WHOLE ACOUSTIC SET ON YOUTUBE LINK IN BIO🙏🏼🖤💛🎸🥁🎷✌🏼🎶

node.text: Sunday candy 🍫 On mans search for meaning the road is long, winding and full of terrors. But this I know. Within pain, there beauty lies. There her purpose is found. To me, it’s this matter that maketh man. I admire women and their beauty. Not just in the physical, but more so in the mental. A sharp tenacity there is in the eyes of a woman. A strength men cannot attain, only seek.
